---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="服務項目 | YENZ Design" description="艷世設計提供品牌識別、視覺設計、網站開發與虛擬形象設計服務。">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-content">
      <span class="page-hero-label">SERVICES</span>
      <h1 class="page-hero-title">全方位品牌解決方案</h1>
      <p class="page-hero-subtitle">Comprehensive Brand Solutions</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Intro -->
  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div class="services-intro reveal">
      <p class="intro-text">
        艷世，讓您的品牌驚艷世界。<br>
        我們為您的品牌量身打造卓越的視覺敘事與數位體驗。<br>
        從核心識別到虛擬場域，每一處皆是精雕細琢，旨在成就您的非凡。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Service 1: Brand Identity -->
  <section class="section section-gradient" id="branding">
    <div class="service-detail">
      <div class="service-detail-header reveal">
        <span class="service-number">01</span>
        <h2 class="service-detail-title">BRAND IDENTITY</h2>
        <p class="service-detail-subtitle">品牌識別策略</p>
        <p class="service-tagline">讓品牌，成為一種信仰</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-detail-content reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p class="service-desc-full">
          我們深入探究您的品牌精髓，將其凝練為一套獨一無二、富有靈魂的識別系統。
          從標誌的點睛之筆，到完整的視覺語彙與品牌故事的昇華呈現，
          每一細節皆精雕細琢，確保您的品牌於市場中，綻放無可取代的卓然光采。
        </p>
        
        <div class="service-items">
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◇</span>
            <span class="item-text">品牌命名與定位</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◇</span>
            <span class="item-text">標誌設計 Logo Design</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◇</span>
            <span class="item-text">視覺識別系統 VIS</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◇</span>
            <span class="item-text">品牌故事撰寫</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◇</span>
            <span class="item-text">品牌規範手冊</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Service 2: Visual Design -->
  <section class="section section-dark" id="visual">
    <div class="service-detail">
      <div class="service-detail-header reveal">
        <span class="service-number">02</span>
        <h2 class="service-detail-title">VISUAL DESIGN</h2>
        <p class="service-detail-subtitle">視覺傳達設計</p>
        <p class="service-tagline">藝術與策略的視覺盛宴</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-detail-content reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p class="service-desc-full">
          艷世將您的品牌訊息，昇華為一場觸動心弦的視覺敘事。
          從精緻的印刷品到動感的影音媒介，乃至數位廣告與各類行銷素材，
          我們以匠心獨具的多元形式，完美演繹品牌魅力。
        </p>
        
        <div class="service-items">
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◈</span>
            <span class="item-text">名片設計</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◈</span>
            <span class="item-text">海報與 DM 設計</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◈</span>
            <span class="item-text">包裝設計</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◈</span>
            <span class="item-text">社群素材設計</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◈</span>
            <span class="item-text">廣告視覺設計</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Service 3: Digital Experience -->
  <section class="section section-gradient" id="digital">
    <div class="service-detail">
      <div class="service-detail-header reveal">
        <span class="service-number">03</span>
        <h2 class="service-detail-title">DIGITAL EXPERIENCE</h2>
        <p class="service-detail-subtitle">數位體驗</p>
        <p class="service-tagline">優雅的互動藝術</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-detail-content reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p class="service-desc-full">
          在數位場域，我們為您的品牌打造的不僅是網站，更是連繫核心客戶的優雅橋樑。
          以使用者為中心，融合頂級美學與直覺功能，
          我們悉心雕琢每一個介面與互動流程，讓每一次點擊，都是一次非凡的品牌沉浸。
        </p>
        
        <div class="service-items">
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◎</span>
            <span class="item-text">網站設計與開發</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◎</span>
            <span class="item-text">UI/UX 設計</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◎</span>
            <span class="item-text">響應式網頁設計</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◎</span>
            <span class="item-text">電商網站</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">◎</span>
            <span class="item-text">互動體驗設計</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Service 4: Virtual World -->
  <section class="section section-dark" id="virtual">
    <div class="service-detail">
      <div class="service-detail-header reveal">
        <span class="service-number">04</span>
        <h2 class="service-detail-title">VIRTUAL WORLD</h2>
        <p class="service-detail-subtitle">虛擬世界</p>
        <p class="service-tagline">拓展維度的品牌敘事</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="service-detail-content reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <p class="service-desc-full">
          面對元宇宙與 AI 浪潮，艷世引領您的品牌，探索全新互動維度。
          從精緻的 VTuber 角色塑造，到栩栩如生的 LIVE2D 動態呈現，
          我們運用尖端虛擬技術，為您的品牌賦予生命。
        </p>
        
        <div class="service-items">
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">❖</span>
            <span class="item-text">VTuber 角色設計</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">❖</span>
            <span class="item-text">Live2D 建模</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">❖</span>
            <span class="item-text">虛擬形象企劃</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">❖</span>
            <span class="item-text">IP 角色開發</span>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="item-icon">❖</span>
            <span class="item-text">動畫製作</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2 class="cta-title reveal">準備好開始您的品牌之旅了嗎？</h2>
    <a href="/contact" class="btn reveal reveal-delay-1">CONTACT US</a>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Page Hero */
  .page-hero {
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--forest-darkest) 0%, var(--forest-dark) 100%);
    padding-top: 100px;
  }
  
  .page-hero-label {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.4em;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .page-hero-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .page-hero-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  }
  
  /* Services Intro */
  .services-intro {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .intro-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 2.2;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  
  /* Service Detail */
  .service-detail {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .service-detail-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }
  
  .service-number {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    opacity: 0.5;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .service-detail-title {
    font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .service-detail-subtitle {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .service-tagline {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--white);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }
  
  .service-detail-content {
    
  }
  
  .service-desc-full {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    line-height: 2.2;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  
  .service-items {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .service-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.2rem 1.5rem;
    background: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .service-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(201, 169, 98, 0.08);
  }
  
  .item-icon {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  
  .item-text {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif TC', serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }
</style>
